{"tid":46171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"霧霾帶來五大意外收獲：讓中國人更團結","createTime":"2016-12-19T12:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T06:38:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bee992d457603e322c6cf752ec039747aca8eb3","tid":46171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:58:14.000Z","msg":"央視網(記者王磊 報道) 毀健康，遮藍天，癱交通&hellip;&hellip;霧霾這兩年成了全民公敵，人人恨不得「食其肉，寢其皮」，逐之於國門之外。然而，能擊潰這個頑敵的似乎不是大內高手，也不是江湖遊俠，而只有來自塞外的風。「風，是北京的抹布。西伯利亞，是北京的清潔工。讓西伯利亞的西北風快些到來吧！」@老徐時評 [email protected]�，也說出了民眾的無奈與自嘲。 <br />\n<br />\n　　不過，你可曾意識到，讓你既痛恨又無奈的霧霾並非一無是處，它在肆虐神州的同時，也給我們民族和個人帶來了五大好處。我沒有瘋，也從未拿過霧霾的賄賂，甚至在寫這篇稿時心髒還隱隱作痛，只是公道話還得說。 <br />\n<br />\n　　首先，霧霾讓中國人更團結。在咱們這個文明古國，各地在千百年變遷過程中形成了自身的傳統和驕傲，加之當代中國地區發展不平衡與大規模人口流動並存，傳媒又日益發達，於是代表不同地方的人互相看不順眼，總拿自己的長處去嘲笑別人的短處，地域攻擊成為「顯學」。在霧霾問題上，最初也不例外。或許這跟曝光度有關，或許跟人們「看熱鬧不怕事大」的心理有關，以北京為代表的一線城市首先成為其他地方人民的攻擊對象。有人借用清華大學校訓杜撰出「厚德載霧，自強不吸」的「北京霧霾精神」&hellip;&hellip;各種半真不假的段子，不勝枚舉。連外國人也來湊熱鬧，創造了個「北京咳」的病症，還渲染中外白領因霧霾紛紛逃離北上廣的「恐慌」。一時間，大家似乎找到了共同的笑柄和出氣筒，人人數落北京，全然不顧首都總體的空氣質量遠強於石家莊、邯鄲、保定、鄭州和蘭州等城市的事實。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com.hk/opinion/highlights/2013-12/2094384.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com.hk%2Fopinion%2Fhighlights%2F2013-12%2F2094384.html&d=NDWZRScc85CluF0EinSSxZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=4868eaa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com.hk/opinion/highlights/2013-12/2094384.html</a>"},{"pid":"fcab7bcceec37da05b6f14453d6c4013d77adaef","tid":46171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099827c3ce38797a157951f2988517d7ec75dc4f","tid":46171,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線"},{"pid":"4a79cc9780bb9b5d76e57d4898dc0b199e556bfd","tid":46171,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42825402bbbeaa100b9a01bae4ecb46d4cbc5ed9","tid":46171,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7f076cb3cb22a9385302c136c6dadb30b73bfe","tid":46171,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:24:48.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com.hk/opinion/highlights/2013-12/2094384.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com.hk%2Fopinion%2Fhighlights%2F2013-12%2F2094384.html&d=NDWZRScc85CluF0EinSSxZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=4868eaa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com.hk/opinion/highlights/2013-12/2094384.html</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n吸多啲啦 蝗蟲 ， 咪撚吹黎香港呀屌"},{"pid":"9d48cb40c41218d8a6638b44d1a153dc6a204440","tid":46171,"uid":57273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:25:20.000Z","msg":"識打一定係咁打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2b5b9b8a080c72b78c1ed045600a9b0c3a1d7c","tid":46171,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"咁。。。。希望殘體國由年頭團結到年尾唔好停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf98f35e6f52f6692f82fe15ea37ef4d642598fc","tid":46171,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"呢樣野未來可能令全國人民團起反共<br />\n繼續封鎖唔比人抗議啦"},{"pid":"de15f5d43e90c889f230b3c114d967eb68f195c3","tid":46171,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"中國境內霧霾，国人或成最大嬴家？"},{"pid":"b99d7fb22d8f4491418a8b0efaa4f39144460a63","tid":46171,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"